### Search Sample API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000/api/samples

### Test 1: Search with pagination only
POST http://localhost:5027/api/samples/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

### Test 2: Search by gender and age range
POST http://localhost:5027/api/samples/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gender": "Male",
  "minAge": 25,
  "maxAge": 50,
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

### Test 3: Search by keyword
POST http://localhost:5027/api/samples/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "keyword": "sample",
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 15
}

### Test 4: Search by city and status
POST http://localhost:5027/api/samples/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "city": "Homs",
  "status": "single",
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

### Test 5: Search by tags
POST http://localhost:5027/api/samples/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tagIds": [1],
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

### Test 6: Advanced search with all filters
POST http://localhost:5027/api/samples/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gender": "Female",
  "minAge": 30,
  "maxAge": 45,
  "city": "damascus",
  "status": "single",
  //"keyword": "eye",
  //"tagIds": [1, 4],
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 20
}

### Test 7: Navigate to page 2
POST http://localhost:5027/api/samples/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "keyword": "sample",
  "page": 2,
  "pageSize": 10
}

### Test 8: Custom page size
POST http://localhost:5027/api/samples/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 50
}

### Test 9: INVALID - Page must be >= 1 (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:5027/api/samples/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "page": 0,
  "pageSize": 10
}

### Test 10: INVALID - PageSize must be <= 100 (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:5027/api/samples/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 200
}

### Test 11: Empty search (all samples)
POST http://localhost:5027/api/samples/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}
